{
  "text": "Let me put it this way, have I laid, have I made missteps in my analysis of what has led to the construction of the archetypes that we experience. I am Ray share with you the observation that judgment is no part of interaction between mind, body, spirit complexes. We have attempted to answer each query as fully as your language and the extent of your previous information allow, we may suggest that if in perusing this present material you have further queries refining any concept. These queries may be asked, and again we shall attempt adequate rejoiners.",
